{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/background-position-fixed-and-cover-with-css/","webpackCompilationHash":"","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I wanted to make a section of a website have a div featuring a background image that had both <code class=\"language-text\">background-attachment: fixed</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">background-size: cover</code>, regardless of the image's size. <a href=\"http://hub51chicago.com/private-parties\">This website</a> is a working example of multiple fixed, full-screen background image divs.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://codepen.io/taniarascia/pen/VpGXJQ\">Demo</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 90vh<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> no-repeat<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> cover<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-attachment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fixed<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>You can also write this code in the <code class=\"language-text\">background</code> shorthand:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>file.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> no-repeat 50% fixed / cover<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Then you'd simply add the background image to the div and adjust the <code class=\"language-text\">height</code> property as necessary.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>file.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>file.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>file.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>I'm only loading the background image in the HTML in the case that you're pulling the image dynamically via PHP. Otherwise, you can create separate classes with background images in the CSS file.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">fixed</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">cover</code> didn't use to play well together, and you would have to put the <code class=\"language-text\">height</code> property in an outer container, but I tested this code on Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Opera, and it works fine.</p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"I wanted to make a section of a website have a div featuring a background image that had both  and , regardless of the image's size. Thisâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"Background Position Fixed and Cover with CSS","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":150,"height":150,"src":"/static/695197f9845f4e2da7a3da0e77e784f4/4148e/css.png","srcSet":"/static/695197f9845f4e2da7a3da0e77e784f4/4148e/css.png 1x"}}},"slug":"background-position-fixed-and-cover-with-css","date":"2017-03-27T00:00:00.000Z","categories":["Design"],"tags":["css"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/background-position-fixed-and-cover-with-css/","date":"2017-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/background-position-fixed-and-cover-with-css/"}}}